    <h3>Financial Officer, UIC SAFC</h3>
    <p>Manage an annual budget exceeding $150,000, ensuring proper allocation, compliance, and financial oversight, and evaluate organizational documents and protocols to inform funding decisions for student organizations. Analyze and organize financial data for SAFC reviews, delivering timely reports to support funding decisions. Collaborate with the Center for Student Involvement to monitor cash flow, ticket accounting, and evaluate funding proposals.</p>
